    • it.polimi.ingsw.ps19.controller.action.MessageInterpreterVisitorImp

    public class MessageInterpreterVisitorImp
extends java.lang.Object
implements MessageInterpreterVisitor
    The Class MessageInterpreterVisitorImp is an implementation of MessageInterpreterVisitor For each message i use Getter to get all attributes of the message and create a specific Action.
